  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Proposal for a temporary transitional power to be exercised by UK regulators
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This publication set out HM Treasury’s proposal for a temporary transitional tool to be exercised by the UK regulators.</p>

  </div>
</div>

